                     <interp inst="t18650410-477-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="animalTheft"></interp>Stealing a mare, the property of <persName id="t18650410-name-587" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18650410-name-587" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
